scenes.description: Opening of the song 'Music Wizard of OZ' with Aki Rosenthal and chibi Hololive members.
Aki Rosenthal performs a solo segment of the song.
The Scarecrow segment of the song featuring Omaru Polka as the Scarecrow.
The Tin Woodman segment of the song featuring AZKi as the Tin Woodman.
